graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
    end

    subgraph "Per DSPA Instance Components"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>REST/gRPC Service<br/>8888/HTTP, 8887/gRPC, 8443/HTTPS]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent<br/>Status Sync]
        ScheduledWorkflow[Scheduled Workflow Controller<br/>Cron-based Scheduling]

        subgraph "Optional Components"
            MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>StatefulSet<br/>3306/TCP]
            Minio[Minio<br/>S3-compatible Storage<br/>9000/TCP]
            MLPUI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>Unsupported/Dev Only]

            subgraph "MLMD Stack"
                MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy<br/>8080/gRPC]
                MLMDgRPC[MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/gRPC]
                MLMDWriter[MLMD Writer]
            end
        end
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|deploys| APIServer
    Controller -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|deploys| ScheduledWorkflow
    Controller -->|deploys if enabled| MariaDB
    Controller -->|deploys if enabled| Minio
    Controller -->|deploys if enabled| MLPUI
    Controller -->|deploys if enabled| MLMDEnvoy
    Controller -->|deploys if enabled| MLMDgRPC
    Controller -->|deploys if enabled| MLMDWriter

    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    APIServer -->|creates pipeline runs| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton]
    APIServer -->|tracks metadata| MLMDEnvoy

    PersistenceAgent -->|syncs status| MariaDB
    PersistenceAgent -->|watches runs| Tekton

    ScheduledWorkflow -->|creates scheduled runs| Tekton
    ScheduledWorkflow -->|reads schedules| MariaDB

    MLMDEnvoy -->|forwards to| MLMDgRPC
    MLMDgRPC -->|stores metadata| MariaDB

    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| APIServer
    Elyra[Elyra Notebooks] -->|pipeline authoring| APIServer

    APIServer -.->|exposes| Route[OpenShift Route<br/>443/HTTPS + OAuth]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style APIServer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
